<taxonomicName LSID="http://zoobank.org/49EABF65-9F2F-482B-B545-B1A997AE9957" authority="trib. nov. [Leaf-like Cladonotinae of Madagascar]" authorityName="trib. nov. [Leaf-like Cladonotinae of Madagascar]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Morphopoides" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Orthoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Valalyllini">Valalyllini trib. nov. [Leaf-like Cladonotinae of Madagascar]</taxonomicName>
